Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.34,0:00:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.65,0:00:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去对您的诸多无礼\N还请见谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.81,0:00:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.60,0:01:11.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.90,0:01:15.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.57,0:01:22.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:29.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.85,0:01:34.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.46,0:01:43.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.37,0:01:58.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.81,0:02:06.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.09,0:02:13.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.19,0:02:24.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}突破作战\NBreakthrough
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一手不需要考虑这么久吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼你的心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何显得很乱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简单的说，副舰长她身分尊贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她回到官廷里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是就会变成我们的敌人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以后到底会怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成死路一条吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道副舰长她不是那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不快埋头干活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，莫蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛一副要死不活的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你还想\N高攀人家副舰长吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位…请问你们\N都是为了什么而登上这艘船呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了出人头地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了过更好的生活\N才来当船员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.50,0:04:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无聊话少说，快干活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是个枪兵耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以在这里扫地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，男儿当自强哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次换了小帅哥上场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问…苏菲亚在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下刚才已经离舰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说殿下是指…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，你不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长她是皇帝的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来是不可能\N不过这的确是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说她上船原本是为了\N负责监视舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果却对舰长一见钟情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活生生一部官廷罗曼史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他好歹也来送人家一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭他的个性甭想啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下又是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能说他正值青春期啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，终于找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你到哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待…待会儿再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士你好怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回帝都去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是不会挽留我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有挽留你的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的打算除掉戴芬妮总帅吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为了这个才活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉丝她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不阻止苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.87,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚她很想和你在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什么都没搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦德赛舰队\N已经和度西斯碰上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下就可以把度西斯的残党…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万万不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了祖国的度西斯舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好比是一头受伤的狮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他们出手是很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了吗，马留司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.11,0:07:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是消灭度西斯\N千载难逢的大好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，请您以您的慈悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.95,0:07:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赐予度西斯人民一块居留地\N才是上上之策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朕刚才已经把\N度西斯派来的使者给斩首了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事，马留司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要阻止也来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朕命你闭门思过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你变了不少呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.39,0:08:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不好比较喜欢现在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莫蓝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是枪兵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在很多战舰上都打过仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.59,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布留纳克号，艾斯塔号\N克劳索拉斯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还是位历经沙场的勇士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道枪兵的生存率是多少吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有区区的三成耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是说只要上了三次战场\N绝大部份都难以幸存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而几次走过死亡边缘\N最后换来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不过就是…这个而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我…一起下船呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我是还没开始\N就已经出局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，请你忘了我说的话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是来解决上次那件事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞧瞧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是下到这一步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚\N苏菲亚她到我房间来找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵升变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一来兵就成了皇后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想该是进攻基尔特的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是强硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要解决掉敌方的国王\N一切就可以结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，该说是皇后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你还有时间去管黑子的皇后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你还是应该先守好\N你身边的白子皇后才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.05,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快带着拉薇下船去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他打算要\N直冲基尔特公会的本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那塔琪安娜你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能待的地方也只有这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.68,0:11:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，我们已经失去了故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们唯一的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这片土地上\N建立一个新的度西斯国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要向安那托勒\N下最后的决战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了死去的同胞们\N我们必须要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次重建我们的光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为度西斯而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为度西斯而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜大人就任乌尔班号舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.49,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这船坐起来挺舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架身分不明的大型货柜\N进到了我方的防空领域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把它给我打下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不发出停船警告\N就直接开炮恐怕不妥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是庆祝我新官上任不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别啰嗦快打就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备炮击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有皇帝的徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那不是\N苏菲亚殿下的御用专机吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止炮击，快停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下驾到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉丝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下您看来身体依然健朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要怎么解释\N您协助银之战舰叛乱一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是叛乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是陛下有四艘战舰遭到击沈\N又该怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为对方主动攻击\N才不得不应战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是强辩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许无礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，度西斯已毁于严寒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我安那托勒也正受到酷热侵袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是打仗的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,务请陛下重新考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思我都听明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.02,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有这份爱民之心与温柔善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为父的感觉十分高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:14:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你想要给大家的这瓶水\N却偏偏只有一份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.90,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这瓶水留给本国的人民\N是身为一国之君的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚，你的行为不端\N将陷为父的于不义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.61,0:14:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把苏菲亚送到塔上关起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊，父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是马留司吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您没有受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，但是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不该让您一个人\N背负这么大的重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.39,0:15:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N这样我回来就没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论在何处\N我总是什么忙都帮不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从女儿死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.11,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直就把你视如己出\N来抚养长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这一切也只到今天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马留司…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您答应我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.99,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您一定要登上王位\N好接下我未完成的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一切结束之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就请苏菲亚殿下您先待在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您不要把爱只献给一个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要献给全民百姓才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马留司…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有话就快说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为\N拉薇你离开这艘船会比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯他似乎打算\N要进攻基尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此我们就一起离开嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.14,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想弄清楚\N这片天空到底发生了什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要攻打基尔特那正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.52,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用爸爸他们的先锋艇\N来飞越大风暴区吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.09,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…并不是爸爸他们的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.26,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这架先锋艇\N当初是亚力克斯驾驶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直瞒着你，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.68,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以余生来说\N这也算是活得够久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是度西斯的残存舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷推进力下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击指挥室连络中断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左满舵，全速脱离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.24,0:17:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让乌尔班号\N被击沈在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左满舵，全速脱离中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然胆敢用夜袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌尔班号到底在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会发生这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来度西斯的主力军\N趁着黑夜全集合到帝都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不用你说也看得出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨炮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去帝都会被攻陷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请陛下禅位给苏菲亚殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻退位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初朕拔擢了\N被基尔特赶出来的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给了你今天的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你居然要恩将仇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.01,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个城市…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是父王的命令吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六号准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七号准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八号准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已进入射程范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.77,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等皇官遭到占领后\N再来攻击就太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一发，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆瓜，命令已经失效了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我，苏菲亚殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次见到您是在官校里吧\N公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是个靠得住的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已准备好一艘\N比银之战舰更高档的战舰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来，我给你一个新任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着这群蝼蚁，还真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要收回组件吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随他们去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.89,0:21:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，我一直在等您回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前任舰长呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落荒而逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以重新把乌尔班号交给我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.81,0:21:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是苏菲亚殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久她就是皇帝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不晓得该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.83,0:21:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得这道伤痕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是当初在练习时\N撞到畜栏所留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.93,0:21:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是在比赛时\N刮到墙壁留下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小家伙并不属于其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是我们的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.41,0:22:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论任何时候\N克劳士你总是会笔直看着目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起飞越大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们从小的梦想吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你现在却表现得婆婆妈妈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.83,0:22:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样的克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.02,0:22:40.18,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.79,0:22:46.85,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.93,0:22:58.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.07,0:23:03.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.68,0:23:12.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.46,0:23:18.33,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.39,0:23:24.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.20,0:23:30.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.07,0:23:35.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.85,0:23:47.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回预告）\N这件维修服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.56,0:23:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一针一线细心缝好的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.60,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.23,0:24:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害唷，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缝这个地方的时候很费工夫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对，我不是要说这个啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.64,0:24:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，你的衣服上\N怎么会有苏菲亚的味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.91,0:24:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.54,0:24:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第17话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.41,0:24:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,备齐材料\NMaking material
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有迪奥和盖尔的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.22,0:24:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
